{"tid":502054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴評迪布尼：訓練懶散 害怕競爭的人","createTime":"2017-12-17T13:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T03:23:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"600956e83c0066bd0b41877854823796099871b0","tid":502054,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rhSBNPl7Kin5egguP2KbmP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=07831eeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】對於被前車路士主帥摩連奴批評為人懶散，曼城中場奇雲迪布尼不以為然回應：「我曾要求公開操練證明被誣陷。」<br />\n<br />\n比利時國腳奇雲迪布尼（Kevin De Bruyne）5年前加盟車路士，英超僅正選上陣兩場，隨後被賣到禾夫斯堡，再在2015年以5500萬鎊加盟曼城。<br />\n<br />\n談到被摩連奴批評，迪布尼反擊道：「他對傳媒說過這些東西，但都是他的一面之詞，因為當時的操練全都是閉門進行，我敢說所有人都知道我不是懶惰的人。」<br />\n<br />\n「我從沒令任何人感到失望，當時我沒甚麼可做，摩連奴大可說我講大話，但我曾要求公開訓練，讓公眾作出判斷。」25歲的迪布尼接受《法國足球》雜誌訪問暢所欲言。"},{"pid":"7d36d56dcf773c311158850137dfcdbf8fa65e7b","tid":502054,"uid":128219,"like":10,"dislike":31,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a96f26f18c2bfb86b3830cf7d16240c24ddf096f","tid":502054,"uid":103947,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"無巴士佬比d考驗你邊有今日咁勁<br />\n做人都唔識知恩圖報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff36f69d80a2271c74500217cc861bb327e00d28","tid":502054,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"摩連奴又然"},{"pid":"862e7d5ae6457614fd09644ddbc2c302ca07933e","tid":502054,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"條撚樣好撚小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c68dc6fa5d17a7043b5308e3f63117f2df5b80","tid":502054,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"真係你有你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9